<DocumentLayout title="Security | TerribleTurtles" description="Security architecture of TerribleTurtles.">
  <h1>Security</h1>
  <p>The TerribleTurtles platform itself is built on a 100% static architecture and served directly from Cloudflare's global edge network.</p>
  <p>There are no databases to inject and no runtime secrets to leak. It sits behind Enterprise-grade DDoS protection and strict Content Security Policies.</p>
